SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250
COMMIT

	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\

	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\

	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\

	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250
SHOW GLOBAL STATUS

SELECT EVENT_NAME, COUNT_STAR, SUM_TIMER_WAIT\
	  FROM performance_schema.events_waits_summary_global_by_event_name

SELECT\
		    TABLE_SCHEMA,\
		    TABLE_NAME,\
		    TABLE_TYPE,\
		    ifnull(ENGINE, 'NONE') as ENGINE,\
		    ifnull(VERSION, '0') as VERSION,\
		    ifnull(ROW_FORMAT, 'NONE') as ROW_FORMAT,\
		    ifnull(TABLE_ROWS, '0') as TABLE_ROWS,\
		    ifnull(DATA_LENGTH, '0') as DATA_LENGTH,\
		    ifnull(INDEX_LENGTH, '0') as INDEX_LENGTH,\
		    ifnull(DATA_FREE, '0') as DATA_FREE,\
		    ifnull(CREATE_OPTIONS, 'NONE') as CREATE_OPTIONS\
		  FROM information_schema.tables\
		  WHERE TABLE_SCHEMA = 'sys'
Quit

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\

	    DIGEST,\

	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT OBJECT_SCHEMA, OBJECT_NAME, ifnull(INDEX_NAME, 'NONE') as INDEX_NAME,\
	    COUNT_FETCH, COUNT_INSERT, COUNT_UPDATE, COUNT_DELETE,\
	    SUM_TIMER_FETCH, SUM_TIMER_INSERT, SUM_TIMER_UPDATE, SUM_TIMER_DELETE\
	  FROM performance_schema.table_io_waits_summary_by_index_usage\
	  WHERE OBJECT_SCHEMA NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema')

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

		    COALESCE(command,'') AS command,\

		    count(*) AS processes,\
		    sum(time) AS seconds\

		  GROUP BY user,SUBSTRING_INDEX(host, ':', 1),command,state\

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250
COMMIT

		    TABLE_SCHEMA,\

		    TABLE_TYPE,\
		    ifnull(ENGINE, 'NONE') as ENGINE,\
		    ifnull(VERSION, '0') as VERSION,\
		    ifnull(ROW_FORMAT, 'NONE') as ROW_FORMAT,\
		    ifnull(TABLE_ROWS, '0') as TABLE_ROWS,\
		    ifnull(DATA_LENGTH, '0') as DATA_LENGTH,\
		    ifnull(INDEX_LENGTH, '0') as INDEX_LENGTH,\
		    ifnull(DATA_FREE, '0') as DATA_FREE,\
		    ifnull(CREATE_OPTIONS, 'NONE') as CREATE_OPTIONS\
		  FROM information_schema.tables\
		  WHERE TABLE_SCHEMA = 'sys'

SELECT\
		    user,\
		    SUBSTRING_INDEX(host, ':', 1) AS host,\
		    COALESCE(command,'') AS command,\
		    COALESCE(state,'') AS state,\
		    count(*) AS processes,\
		    sum(time) AS seconds\
		  FROM information_schema.processlist\
		  WHERE ID != connection_id()\
		    AND TIME >= 0\
		  GROUP BY user,SUBSTRING_INDEX(host, ':', 1),command,state\
		  ORDER BY null

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250
COMMIT

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

		    user,\
		    SUBSTRING_INDEX(host, ':', 1) AS host,\
		    COALESCE(command,'') AS command,\
		    COALESCE(state,'') AS state,\
		    count(*) AS processes,\
		    sum(time) AS seconds\
		  FROM information_schema.processlist\
		  WHERE ID != connection_id()\
		    AND TIME >= 0\
		  GROUP BY user,SUBSTRING_INDEX(host, ':', 1),command,state\
		  ORDER BY null

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

	    COUNT_FETCH, COUNT_INSERT, COUNT_UPDATE, COUNT_DELETE,\
	    SUM_TIMER_FETCH, SUM_TIMER_INSERT, SUM_TIMER_UPDATE, SUM_TIMER_DELETE\

SELECT\
		    user,\
		    SUBSTRING_INDEX(host, ':', 1) AS host,\
		    COALESCE(command,'') AS command,\
		    COALESCE(state,'') AS state,\
		    count(*) AS processes,\
		    sum(time) AS seconds\
		  FROM information_schema.processlist\
		  WHERE ID != connection_id()\
		    AND TIME >= 0\
		  GROUP BY user,SUBSTRING_INDEX(host, ':', 1),command,state\
		  ORDER BY null

	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250
